     <h1>
      About Anchor Flooring Ltd
     </h1>
     <img class="alignright img-br" alt="workers" src="images/workers.jpg" />
     <p>
      Based in Lancashire, Anchor Flooring Ltd has been established since 
			1995 and has been supplying flooring services to the Health service, 
			Local authorities, Education department, Universities, Hotel and 
			hospitality sector, contract and commercial industry for nearly 15 
			years. We currently employ full time fitters, with experience ranging 
			from 12 to 25 years!
     </p>
